Company Description
 
Roofstock, Inc. provides an online marketplace that allows investors to invest in leased investment homes from institutional sellers. It operates Roofstock, a technology-enabled cloud-delivered platform that brings together players from the single-family rental industry under one roof to buy and sell homes.


