Rental Property Investing for Listen Money Matters
































































Roofstock 
Roofstock’s innovative online marketplace allows anyone to buy and sell certified, leased Single-Family Rental properties using our transparent, efficient and easy-to-use platform.
















Sign-up for this exclusive offer for Listen Money Matters listeners









In partnership with
 
 
The Listen Money Matters team of Andrew Fiebert and Thomas Frank have built their reputation on providing their listeners with honest financial advice based on their own personal investing experiences.
Listen Money Matters recommends Roofstock’s innovative marketplace as a great way to discover Single-Family Rental properties that generate cash flow from day one.
Exclusive Offer
For a limited time only, Roofstock is offering Listen Money Matters listeners a special promotion by waiving the Roofstock Marketplace transaction fee on your next investment property purchase. You must register for this offer before July 31st, 2017 to qualify. To get started, fill out the form on this page to become eligible and begin browsing cash flowing rental homes! See Terms & Conditions* for full details.



























Roofstock makes investing in Single-Family Rental houses easier than ever.

Consistent Cash Flow: With tenants in place, you start generating income immediately and avoid losing rent during a sale
Transparency: Property certification, inspection reports and diligence documentation allow you to invest with confidence
Cost-Effective: We negotiate fair pricing based on accurate property valuations, while reducing broker fees and closing costs
Expert Advice: Our team of advisors help you use our power tools to identify the right investment property and guide you through the transaction
Exclusive Inventory: Our marketplace of Single-Family Rental houses offers access to off-market properties not listed on the MLS
 
*Offer Terms & Conditions:
You must register for this offer before July 31st, 2017 to qualify. To become eligible to have your Roofstock Marketplace Transaction fee waived on your next investment property purchase, you must fill out the form above and provide a valid email address.
Marketplace transaction fee will be charged at checkout and refunded when the property closes. Offer valid for the first house purchased with an executed purchase and sale agreement prior to October 31, 2017. Transaction fees will not be refunded if the purchase isn't closed. The Roofstock Marketplace transaction fee is equal to 0.5% of the final sale price of the property. 
Roofstock reserves the right to change the terms and conditions of this offer without notice. By signing up for this offer, you agree to its terms and conditions.




























