Roofstock, Inc.


                  Roofstock, Inc. provides online real estate services. The company offers online marketplace created exclusively for investing in leased single-family rental homes that generate cash flow day one. The firm provides research, analytics, and insights to evaluate and purchase independently certified properties at set prices. The company was founded by Gary Beasley, Gregor Watson, Rich Ford and Devin Wade in 2015 and is headquartered in Oakland, CA.                





