Rental Property Investing for Investor Junkie Readers


































































Roofstock
Roofstock’s innovative online marketplace allows anyone to buy and sell certified, leased Single-Family Rental properties using our transparent, efficient and easy-to-use platform.
















Sign-up for our Limited Time Offer and start investing!









In partnership with 
 
Investor Junkie recommends Roofstock as an investment platform that simplifies the process of building a rental property portfolio through its efficient and transparent marketplace, making the Single-Family Rental market more accessible to investors of all types.
Limited Time Offer: First-time Roofstock customers can sign-up for a reduced marketplace transaction fee of $99 on their first investment property purchase!*



























Roofstock makes investing in Single-Family Rental houses easier than ever.

Consistent Cash Flow: With tenants in place, you start generating income immediately and avoid losing rent during a sale
Transparency: Property certification, inspection reports and diligence documentation allow you to invest with confidence
Cost-Effective: We negotiate fair pricing based on accurate property valuations, while reducing broker fees and closing costs
Expert Advice: Our team of advisors help you identify the right investment property and guide you through the transaction
Exclusive Inventory: Our marketplace of Single-Family Rental houses offers access to off-market properties not listed on the MLS

* Roofstock reserves the right to end this promotional offer at any time.Roofstock’s marketplace transaction fee is normally 0.5% of the property sale price.


























