Ready to Innovate with Us?Come Work Under Our Roof.




Working With Us
We’re changing the way real estate works and we’re having a blast doing it! Based in a hip brick open-beam office in Oakland, just a block from BART, with great food and music venues a stone’s throw away, we’re in the heart of the thriving East Bay start-up scene. We work collaboratively, innovate fast, and have a team filled with industry experts and technology super stars. Join us.






Awards and Employee Reviews
Roofstock has been certified as a great workplace by the independent analysts at Great Place to Work® based on ratings provided by our employees in anonymous surveys. Check out our Great Place To Work company review, as well as our Glassdoor page, and see why our employees love working here!
     



